casebody.data:
WALTER WYAHLLYETH v. MARGARET E. WYAHLLYETH [No. 29,

April Term, 1943.]

Decided June 2, 1943.

The cause was argued before Sloan, C. J., Delaplaine, Collins, Marbury, Grason, Melvin, and Adams, JJ.

Jere L. Santry for the appellant.

The court declined to hear argument for the appellee, but Irving D. Grandberg appeared on the brief for the appellee.

Collins, J., delivered the opinion of the Court.
